  "analyst_note": "CVE-2010-4344: Remote heap overflow in Exim SMTP server < 4.70 via crafted string in the log_write() function. Exim exposes its version in the SMTP ESMTP banner (220 hostname ESMTP Exim X.YZ). nmap -sV reliably extracts this. Note: Postfix, Sendmail, qmail, and Exchange will show different MTA names in the banner \u2014 these should be marked not-validated. Fixed: Exim 4.70.",
